Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Haruka's Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This program will introduce the friends that appear in Kotoura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Kotoura Haruka, will make the introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Our guest for episode one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,has spent the last 15 years reading other people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your mind is like an open book to me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please welcome Kotoura Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Kotoura Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I recently transferred into Midorigaoka High School. I'm a first-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the ability to read people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like ESP or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I'd rather not have this ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Kotoura, how does it feel to be able to read people's minds?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In class there's a boy called Manabe who sits next to me and is a lecher to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I get bombarded with his erotic fantasies. It's pretty rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish he'd grow up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Your ability seems useful but it has a downside too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. People just don't seem to get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beat.
